description: Gets a list of all VM scale sets under a resource group.

nextlink.description: The uri to fetch the next page of Virtual Machine Scale Sets. Call ListNext() with this to fetch the next page of VMSS.

value.description: The list of virtual machine scale sets.

resource_group_name.description: The name of the resource group.

subscription_id.description: Subscription credentials which uniquely identify Microsoft Azure subscription. The subscription ID forms part of the URI for every service call.
